text: Joslyn Chavarria (born 18 April 1959) is a Belizean former cyclist. He competed in the individual road race and the team time trial events at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Belizean male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Belize Category:Cyclists at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
